snippet.title: Necrophoresis Trailer 1 - Indie Horror Game
snippet.description:
Necrophoresis is a co-op horror game for 1-4 players. Explore a haunted morgue to find its dark secrets. Use what you can find to make your way through the morgue and find your way out.

Check it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2669540/Necrophoresis/

#gaming #horrorgaming #indiegame #indiegames #steam #steamgame
